The trailer for Trust is out NOW! So excited for you guys to see our film. Out in select theaters and on demand March 12th. 

If you like a tense, sexy rom-dram, you're gonna love #TrustMovie . Trussst me ♥️ 

Check out etonline.com for the official movie poster & more exclusive details (link in bio) 

@trustmovie2021 @matthewdaddario @kat.mcnamara @its_lucien @lindseybroad @ronnychieng @verticalentertainment

node.text:
I know times have been tough for a lot of us, but whatever you’re going through, please know that you don’t have to do it alone. Make your mental health a top priority this year! I know I will be. Too many people are suffering and don’t know who to turn to or how to start. What I love about BetterHelp is that you can get a therapy session from the privacy of your own home. 
Check out the link in my bio for a 20% discount for the first month!! Love you guys & wishing you all nothing but happiness, peace of mind and good health always. 🙏🏼🤍 Xo Vic

node.title: I’m SO excited to be partnering with @betterhelp!

Photo shared by Victoria Justice on August 04, 2021 tagging @spencermusic. May be an image of text that says 'And like Victorious, Afterlife also taps into Justice's musical side. The actor co-wrote one of the film's four original songs, "Home," alongside co-star Spencer Sutherland. The goal was "to write a song that was not a love song, but a life song, and life songs are a ittle bit harder to write because it can just get cheesy easily, you know?" she says. "ButI feel like we really did strike that balance."'.

node.text:
Hi guys!! Just been reflecting on music & what I’ve put out so far & I just felt compelled to say THANK YOU. 
Specifically for my song Treat Myself… it was one that was very personal and special to me. To know that some of you can relate and have embraced this song in your own way is the coolest. 
The fact that I put this song out completely independently & the response has been so wonderful is something I’m proud of.  Thanks for listening and thanks for all your continued support. Means a lot 🥲. 
Oh & follow me on Spotify (if you’d like) to get more music updates in the future. Much love to you all & hope you’re being kind to yourselves & one another🙏🏼😘 *link in bio
